<b>Raging Fury</b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umaslethalo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>maslethalo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(10/4/01 8:24:50 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dueling 60 Wizard with epic</span><hr size=1> Honestly if you lose to a wizard you shouldn't be playing a druid.  A druid should always beat a wizard. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uglittermist.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Glittermist</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(10/9/01 11:53:30 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> How to kill a 60 epic wizard</span><hr size=1> Stock up a few Steele golem wands (5 charges instant right click annull - dropped in Cazik Thule by the steele golem which has a PH, easy camp).  Also there are a few CH items you can use too such as potions that drop from the Ishva Mal in infected paw.<br>
<br>
I am assuming you are going into this fight fully buffed.<br>
If you are not then you better be prepared to F1 + Heal right away depending on your regular resists/what spells he uses.<br>
<br>
Annul bomb him.   Boom got rid of his epic buff, and any other buffs he had up (10 slot annul, so he MAY still have 5 buffs so you might want to bomb him a few extra times from alternate golem wand).  <br>
Ros sundering, and winged death (may need to heal yourself now).  Keep healing if he keeps nuking.<br>
If he goes to annul himself, Scorae him. (I prefer scorae to wildfire because it mostly hits players for more as it seems to be lure based).  Scorae again.  Heal self if needed.  Scorae again.<br>
Wizard starts casting gate or dies.<br>
<br>
Well... it USUALLY happens this way you never know with fluke resistances. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umaslethalo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>maslethalo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(10/9/01 7:16:52 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How to kill a 60 epic wizard</span><hr size=1> screw the wand just use your spell.  annull, annull, annull, WD, Heal, Nuke, Nuke, dead wizard.  I beat a lvl 60 with epic when i was lvl 59.  Wasnt even close. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukenuon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kenuon</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(10/10/01 9:15:38 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: How to kill a 60 epic wizard</span><hr size=1> bah I can't believe you woods and frogs found my post. :p <br>
